div.div:
SheetData{
[rowIdx: number]: {
[colIdx: number]: CellData
}
}
CellData
{
computed: string | number,
raw: string,
error: boolean
}
SheetGraph (DAG - Directed Acyclic Graph)
{
[dependencyCellIdx: rowIdx_colIdx]: dependentCellIdx[ ]
}
dependentCellIdx: rowIdx_colIdx
e.g.
A1 (0, 0): 20
B1 (0, 1): =2*A1
Sheet Graph:
{
"0_0": ["0_1"] // changing A1(0,0) will trigger B1(0,1)
}
dependencies are parent nodes (cells referenced in formulas), and dependents are child nodes (cells containing formulas).
